biography: Florian Jetter started his career at Blue Yonder – JDA Software by building and running machine learning models. Eventually, he got frustrated by slow and inefficient data pipelines and built libraries and tools to support his fellow Data Scientists and Data Engineers. His focus quickly shifted from machine learning to data engineering and he leverages the knowledge of both worlds to build a reliable data platform.
